              <span id="reviewTextContainer2691786142" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13421853240701375402">A simple plot designed to bring individuals completely alien (in the literal, extra-planetary sense of the word) into conversation with one another concerning mathematics, science, and philosophy. Some interesting, ahead-of-their-time ideas, presented with a bit of wry humor. Overall not a fantastic book, but an intriguing example of proto science fiction from 1752</span>

          </span>
        </div>


