        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2988749728" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8766531013602069928">What a beautiful story of human place in grand scheme of things. I had this idea during the reading, it must be the reason why God has this uncollapsible love for us. <br/><br/>For a being so big it&apos;s hard not to find being so small cute and endearing.<br/><br/>Even the evil doesn&apos;t look so bad under the microscope. Which is pretty counterintuitive, if you ask me. Must be wood from trees thing.<br/><br/>And this was written 1752. Holly micro mega shit.</span>
  <span id="freeText8766531013602069928" style="display:none">What a beautiful story of human place in grand scheme of things. I had this idea during the reading, it must be the reason why God has this uncollapsible love for us. <br /><br />For a being so big it's hard not to find being so small cute and endearing.<br /><br />Even the evil doesn't look so bad under the microscope. Which is pretty counterintuitive, if you ask me. Must be wood from trees thing.<br /><br />And this was written 1752. Holly micro mega shit.</span>
  <a data-text-id="8766531013602069928" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


